tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE clients (
  client_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  client_name VARCHAR(50),
  income DECIMAL,
  tax_bracket_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (tax_bracket_id) REFERENCES tax_brackets(bracket_id)
);

CREATE TABLE tax_calculations (
  calculation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  client_id INT NOT NULL,
  taxable_income INT NOT NULL,
  tax_due DECIMAL(8,2) NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (client_id) REFERENCES clients(client_id)
);

CREATE TABLE tax_bracket (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    bracket_name VARCHAR(255),
    lower_threshold DECIMAL,
    upper_threshold DECIMAL,
    tax_rate DECIMAL
);
